    • Field Detail

      • API_SERVER_VERSION

        public static final int[] API_SERVER_VERSION
        Api server version. To check compatibility the difference with the first and third digit must be the same whit the client version. Exemple : Server version 0,1,2 : 0 - 2 = -2 Client version 1,1,3 : 1 - 3 = -2 Client and Server are compatible.
